  <data name="InputTextBoxTooltip.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>The text of this box is used as input for the text generator</value>
  </data>
  <data name="LoadFileButtonTooltip.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Load the content of input text box from a .txt file (actually you can load all kind of data and get some strange result, but rename the extension of file to .txt)</value>
  </data>
  <data name="ExecuteButtonTooltip.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Run the generator! Note: try to increase generator's Top K or result length if you see strange output</value>
  </data>
  <data name="SeparatorTokenizerSeparatorTooltip.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>A **single character** that will divide text in separated tokens</value>
  </data>
  <data name="BlockTokenizerBlockSizeTooltip.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Sets the size of each token</value>
  </data>
  <data name="StageRepeatTimesTooltip.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>How many times to repeat this stage? The input of every next stage is output of previous</value>
  </data>
  <data name="SmartTokenizerIterationsCountTooltip.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Sets the count of iterations. Each iterations creates up to one new token from 2 old. The more this value, the longer tokenization will be. Optimal values are in range [1000..10000]</value>
  </data>
  <data name="OutputTextBoxTooltip.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>This text box contains output of the generator</value>
  </data>
  <data name="SmartTokenizerMaxTokenLengthTooltip.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Sets the max length of a token. Pairs, that make a token with length, greater than this value, can't be merged. If there's no available pairs, the tokenization stops at this moment.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="SelectedTokenizerTooltip.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Selected strategy to create human readable text from tokens graph. Read documentation to learn more about different generator types</value>
  </data>
  <data name="DefaultGeneratorResultLengthTooltip.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Sets the count of tokens that should be generated</value>
  </data>
  <data name="SmartTokenizerTopKTooltip.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Sets the count of most frequent pairs from which 1 will be randomly selected and converted into the next token</value>
  </data>
  <data name="DefaultGeneratorTopKTooltip.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Sets the count of most frequent next tokens from which 1 will be randomly selected and written into the text. Values like 1 or 2 may give strange results</value>
  </data>
  <data name="DefaultGeneratorRandomTokenTooltip.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Sets the chance in range [0..1] of selecting random next token. A value of 1 gives only randomly selected tokens. A value of 0 ensures that only tokens following the previous one are selected (but next token will be randomly generated if there is no subsequent tokens)</value>
  </data>
  <data name="ClearTokenizerCacheTooltip.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Some tokenizers take too long time to create tokens, so Word Degenerator creates cache for the last tokenization. This button clears the cache and tokenizer must do retokenization next generation</value>
  </data>
  <data name="DefaultGeneratorEnableSeparatorTooltip.Text" xml:space="preserve">
